         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-02/huishou_faxinshery.jpg?VersionId=iabuNusdIenm3tlWmNZX2OzdKC2kNIz2&amp;itok=YaeGV-HK" alt="" data-caption="羽生结弦在比赛结束后等待分数的间隙向镜头挥手。（法新社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-02/huishou_faxinshery.jpg?VersionId=iabuNusdIenm3tlWmNZX2OzdKC2kNIz2&amp;itok=YaeGV-HK" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
